Add the following lines to your .emacs file:

(setq load-path (cons "~/.emacs-mode/rml-mode/" load-path))
(setq auto-mode-alist
      (cons '("\\.rml[i]?$" . rml-mode) auto-mode-alist))
(autoload 'rml-mode "rml" "Major mode for editing Rml code." t)
(if window-system (require 'rml-font))


Add in your path the address of the directory where Reactive-ML is installed

